long-term income patterns,

00:03:38.290 --> 00:03:40.970
but has also explored
theoretical possibilities

00:03:40.970 --> 00:03:42.610
for equitable growth.

00:03:42.610 --> 00:03:46.300
He continues to probe the
dynamics of income inequality

00:03:46.300 --> 00:03:49.123
and produce models for optimal taxation.

